{
  "id": "RAW_1014bfae",
  "title": "好莱坞首位 AI 女演员幕后：花 6 万美元「整」出黑眼圈，毙掉 2000 版，卡梅隆：令人毛骨悚然",
  "url": "https://www.ifanr.com/1647967?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=",
  "date": "2025-12-10 17:13:25",
  "author": "姚桐",
  "siteName": "爱范儿",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-MwZPd3bXDohe7txeHOKcLjwJnrf\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;2e0813e1-d147-4461-ad0e-a71f5eae83f6&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:508,&quot;width&quot;:910,&quot;currHeight&quot;:508,&quot;currWidth&quot;:910,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:508,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:910,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FWUoGbToQ4opjjkxXm9LcLmhzndg%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;WUoGbToQ4opjjkxXm9LcLmhzndg&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:589056,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648013\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/img_6939342eed1bc-360x201.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"987\" height=\"551\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/img_6939342eed1bc-360x201.png!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/img_6939342eed1bc-768x429.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/img_6939342eed1bc.png 910w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px\">\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>两个月前，女演员 Tilly Norwood 遭遇了一场「网暴」。</p>\n  <p>《权力的游戏》里的「三傻」苏菲·特纳没给她留一点面子，直接在 Instagram 下留言：「哇……不用你，可谢谢了。」</p>\n  <p>而主演过《傲骨贤妻》的知名演员贝蒂·吉尔平更狠，洋洋洒洒写了几千字的公开信，嘲讽 Tilly 「不是人」，让她「回家」。</p>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-R89vd6OyioclJDxY4UPcZuytngg\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;b786fbab-8500-419e-b120-0b63e1e91922&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1406,&quot;width&quot;:1125,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1406,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1125,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1406,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1125,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FHJWDbivsqoXeytxJI0Bcfuuon2g%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;HJWDbivsqoXeytxJI0Bcfuuon2g&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1312985,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n     <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-R89vd6OyioclJDxY4UPcZuytngg\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;9e0e22f0-a4a0-45f6-919d-e79ed62c5342&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1406,&quot;width&quot;:1125,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1406,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1125,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1406,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1125,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FHJWDbivsqoXeytxJI0Bcfuuon2g%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;HJWDbivsqoXeytxJI0Bcfuuon2g&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1312985,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n      <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648017\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/image123-360x450.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"981\" height=\"1226\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/image123-360x450.png!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/image123-768x960.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/image123-819x1024.png 819w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/image123.png 1125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 981px) 100vw, 981px\">\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>为什么这么大仇？<strong>因为 Tilly 确实不是人，而是英国公司 Particle6 用 AI 生成的「女演员」。</strong></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/arts-culture/film/tilly-norwood-ai-actress-particle6-d5c51da9\">不过更有意思的是，在《华尔街日报》最近一篇报道里，我们终于看到 Tilly 到底是怎么被「捏」出来的。</a></p>\n  <h3>漫漫造星路，说不上来是哪几个 AI 的混血儿</h3>\n  <p>Tilly 的诞生故事听起来像个段子：那是 Particle6 公司的创始人兼 CEO 范德维尔登（ Eline Van der Velden）在伦敦一家私人俱乐部的洗手间里想出来的。</p>\n  <p>范德维尔登首先求助于 ChatGPT，她输入了一段简短但具体的描述，描绘了她理想中的「候选人」：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p>一位魅力四射、享誉全球的女名人。她五官对称，肌肤光彩照人，拥有一双迷人的绿色眼睛。她有一头长发。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p>ChatGPT 还建议叫她 Tilly Warner，但被范德维尔登否决。经过团队的讨论，最终定名为 Tilly Norwood。团队还特意确认了现实世界中没有同名的公众人物。</p>\n  <p>后来，为了让她能动、能说、能演，Particle6 几乎把市面上最顶尖的 AI 工具用了个遍：Runway、Sora、11Labs、ChatGPT，甚至还包括 DeepSeek。</p>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-NPe3dJr1GooPduxWmn2cHDtInXb\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;471bf17c-7b7f-44a2-a7ca-4025c5a38fc2&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:630,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;currHeight&quot;:630,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:630,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FY0GHbbe2EoVcyox5XO2cXzeEnXl%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;Y0GHbbe2EoVcyox5XO2cXzeEnXl&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:88786,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n     <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-NPe3dJr1GooPduxWmn2cHDtInXb\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;82886930-07a8-415a-a01b-64b45d997823&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:630,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;currHeight&quot;:630,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:630,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FY0GHbbe2EoVcyox5XO2cXzeEnXl%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;Y0GHbbe2EoVcyox5XO2cXzeEnXl&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:88786,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n      <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648023\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/tilly-norwood-ai-actress-1200x630-360x189.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1029\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/tilly-norwood-ai-actress-1200x630-360x189.jpg!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/tilly-norwood-ai-actress-1200x630-768x403.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/tilly-norwood-ai-actress-1200x630-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/tilly-norwood-ai-actress-1200x630.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px\">\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>说实话，Tilly 才是 AI 界的「集大成者」。</p>\n  <p>不仅如此，Sora 2 的发布更是给她送来了「东风」。以前的 AI 视频漏洞百出，现在 Sora 2 已经能做到画面逻辑和一致性的大幅提升。这意味着，Tilly 不仅能活在精修图里，她马上就能进组拍长视频甚至电影。</p>\n  <h3>为了「妈生感」，这位姐花 6 万美元「整容」</h3>\n  <p>范德维尔登在接受采访时透露：<strong>为了捏出这张脸，她带着 15 个人的团队，像疯狂的选角导演一样，毙掉了 2000 个 AI 生成的「练习生」。</strong></p>\n  <p>初代的 Tilly 也曾是个灾难。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648020\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162050-360x355.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"968\" height=\"954\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162050-360x355.png!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162050-768x757.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162050-1024x1010.png 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162050.png 1143w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 968px) 100vw, 968px\"></p>\n  <p>ChatGPT 生成的第一张形象图是卡通风格，嘴唇圆润，眼睛像猕猴桃一样，种族特征模糊不清。或许是因为 AI 参考了世界上黑发人口远多于金发人口的数据，决定把她设定成棕发。</p>\n  <p>范德维尔登不喜欢第一个 Tilly：「它显然非常人工智能化，非常卡通化，这不是我想要的效果。」</p>\n  <p>几天后，范德维尔登将第一张图像输入到一个可以添加新特征的工具中。然而，Tilly 仍然显得不真实。范德维尔登考虑过把她做成半机器人，但那并不是最令人震惊的，她认为 AI 最让人震惊的是它能做到如此逼真。</p>\n  <p>现在的 Tilly，头发有点乱，眼底挂着淡淡的黑眼圈，脸上还有雀斑。<strong>为了实现这一切，范德维尔登自掏腰包花费了超过 6 万美元。</strong></p>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-BC12dmPjHoFQVcxXiGwcJeyZnqd\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;2f6ea0fb-d8fb-4cd7-9fd0-d40052bb806d&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:558.7453874538745,&quot;width&quot;:452,&quot;currHeight&quot;:558.7453874538745,&quot;currWidth&quot;:452,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:670,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:542,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.8339483394833949,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FNB9ZbeAWFod0oBxSd81cV0UunUc%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;NB9ZbeAWFod0oBxSd81cV0UunUc&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:409966,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n     <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-BC12dmPjHoFQVcxXiGwcJeyZnqd\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;959b0c71-851f-4f07-927c-a76a319cb095&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:558.7453874538745,&quot;width&quot;:452,&quot;currHeight&quot;:558.7453874538745,&quot;currWidth&quot;:452,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:670,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:542,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.8339483394833949,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FNB9ZbeAWFod0oBxSd81cV0UunUc%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;NB9ZbeAWFod0oBxSd81cV0UunUc&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:409966,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n      <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n       <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-EzUtduZiRooAuixdAPdchhQwnjf\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;b52d7300-68ab-43d8-a8f6-a7a48e2c5fc3&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:670,&quot;width&quot;:542,&quot;currHeight&quot;:670,&quot;currWidth&quot;:542,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:670,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:542,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FQ9lfbThD1oKiAuxovGcclXA1nrg%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;Q9lfbThD1oKiAuxovGcclXA1nrg&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:409966,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n        <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648021\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162217-360x445.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1020\" height=\"1261\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162217-360x445.png!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-09-162217.png 542w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\">\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>更有意思的是，在一次测试中，AI 自作主张给她的无名指戴上了一枚婚戒，使其带有了一种诡异的真实。</p>\n  <h3>Tilly 背后的女人</h3>\n  <p>要说 Tilly 为什么能「火」，还得看她背后的女人范德维尔登。</p>\n  <p>她出身优渥，生在加勒比海的库拉索岛，爸妈是高管和艺术家。她 14 岁就只身闯荡英国，进了著名的特林公园表演艺术学校，跟「灰姑娘」莉莉·詹姆斯、「星战女主」黛西·雷德利是校友。</p>\n  <p>在范德维尔登勇闯好莱坞时，一位洛杉矶的经纪人非常直白地跟她说：「你只要再瘦个 10 磅，整一下外表，你就是下一个布莱克·莱弗利（Blake Lively）。」</p>\n  <p>面对让人下头的身材焦虑和流水线审美，换别人可能就忍了，或者直接抑郁了。但这位姐选择了「发疯」反击。</p>\n  <p>她转头就为 BBC Three 的网剧《Miss Holland》塑造了一个滑稽可笑的选美皇后角色。在名场面里，这位「选美皇后」梳着土气的挤奶女工辫，不仅被廉价美黑喷雾呛得狼狈不堪，更是毫不避讳地展示浓密的腋毛。</p>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-BC12dmPjHoFQVcxXiGwcJeyZnqd\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;2f6ea0fb-d8fb-4cd7-9fd0-d40052bb806d&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:558.7453874538745,&quot;width&quot;:452,&quot;currHeight&quot;:558.7453874538745,&quot;currWidth&quot;:452,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:670,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:542,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.8339483394833949,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FNB9ZbeAWFod0oBxSd81cV0UunUc%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;NB9ZbeAWFod0oBxSd81cV0UunUc&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:409966,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n     <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-VOjbdPMpMoCN6uxK8jtcU5Bun7u\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;94bc0e87-7b52-488d-9fbb-59990c8479e0&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:690,&quot;width&quot;:1175,&quot;currHeight&quot;:690,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1175,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:690,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1175,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FQ87rb0dlroyuSwx3Nu0cvVSenqf%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;Q87rb0dlroyuSwx3Nu0cvVSenqf&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:687130,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n      <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648019\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/025-12-10-141133-360x211.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1008\" height=\"591\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/025-12-10-141133-360x211.png!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/025-12-10-141133-768x451.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/025-12-10-141133-1024x601.png 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/025-12-10-141133.png 1175w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1008px) 100vw, 1008px\">\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>后来，她在伦敦创办 Particle6，很快就开始为 BBC Three 和 YouTube 制作短片，内容包括一些搞笑桥段，比如让身穿比基尼的日光浴者穿上衣服，或者故意靠近陌生人观察会发生什么。</p>\n  <p>这种特立独行的劲头，最后演变成了现在的 Tilly ：既然你们想要完美的流水线产品，那我就直接用代码给你们造一个。</p>\n  <h3>出道即巅峰，黑红也是红</h3>\n  <p>自「签约好莱坞」的消息传出后， Tilly 便陷入了争议之中。</p>\n  <p>英国演员艾米丽·布朗特在参与一档播客期间得知 Tilly，惊呼：我们完蛋了。</p>\n  <p>这种恐惧真不是空穴来风。还记得今年《超人》电影里那只超狗 Krypto 吗？导演本来想让救助犬 Ozu 本色出演，结果成片出来，那就是一只由 CGI 和 AI 重塑的数字狗。</p>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-OUItdMl78oFj1IxTqdEc8moznCe\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;8457f903-1da4-4d2f-ae1d-94a67cf0cc84&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1030,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1030,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1030,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FHuFDbJ5QLoyjTxxrryVc3KEAn0d%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;HuFDbJ5QLoyjTxxrryVc3KEAn0d&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:84256,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n     <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-OUItdMl78oFj1IxTqdEc8moznCe\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;fd1a836b-a524-4cb5-9c7d-0fbb713115a8&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1030,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1030,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1030,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FHuFDbJ5QLoyjTxxrryVc3KEAn0d%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;HuFDbJ5QLoyjTxxrryVc3KEAn0d&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:84256,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n      <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648024\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_Gnp7n2aaMAIErU6-360x309.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"966\" height=\"829\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_Gnp7n2aaMAIErU6-360x309.jpg!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_Gnp7n2aaMAIErU6-768x659.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_Gnp7n2aaMAIErU6-1024x879.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_Gnp7n2aaMAIErU6.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 966px) 100vw, 966px\">\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>真狗都得给假狗让路，何况人呢？</p>\n  <p>2023 年的大罢工核心议题就是 AI 对演员肖像权的侵蚀，而 Tilly 的出现证明，资本甚至不需要剥削真人的肖像，因为他们可以直接凭空创造一个。</p>\n  <p>为什么好莱坞的资本家们对 Tilly 如此上头？原因很现实。</p>\n  <p>就像范德维尔登所说：「当预算在缩水，期望却在不断提高时，你为什么不使用一个能让你用 10% 的成本获得 10 倍产出的工具呢？」</p>\n  <p>Tilly 是完美的打工人，她不需要休息、吃饭，不会生病，更省去了与经纪人扯皮谈片酬的繁琐环节。</p>\n  <p>最重要的是，她没有私生活，不会涉及偷税漏税，也不会因为在网上发表不当言论而遭封杀。</p>\n  <p>相比于之前的虚拟网红仅限于时尚代言 ，Tilly 直接切入了影视表演的关键环节。她不仅有外表，还在构建性格。</p>\n  <p>前几天，范德维尔登问她是否有什么话想对卡梅隆说，这位导演曾公开表示对 AI 演员的想法，她给出了一个充满挑衅意味的回答：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p>噢，真可爱，詹姆斯。（Oh, how cute, James.）</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p>说到这里，就不得不提最近好莱坞发生的另一件大事，Netflix 要花 720 亿美元收购华纳兄弟。</p>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-KNdSdkoMBoQaoMxlL48cYbJgnee\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;53421e48-77c0-4572-955c-edf8edf1c6eb&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:622,&quot;width&quot;:936,&quot;currHeight&quot;:622,&quot;currWidth&quot;:936,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:622,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:936,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FVU4Jb9DFdol48zxFREUccek5nfe%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;VU4Jb9DFdol48zxFREUccek5nfe&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:24071,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n     <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-KNdSdkoMBoQaoMxlL48cYbJgnee\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;bf37ea87-6d6c-4693-b93d-1e79ed4a4ede&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:622,&quot;width&quot;:936,&quot;currHeight&quot;:622,&quot;currWidth&quot;:936,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:622,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:936,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FVU4Jb9DFdol48zxFREUccek5nfe%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;VU4Jb9DFdol48zxFREUccek5nfe&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:24071,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n      <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648025\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_G7Z1oOQb0AQJI0e-1-360x239.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1014\" height=\"673\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_G7Z1oOQb0AQJI0e-1-360x239.jpg!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_G7Z1oOQb0AQJI0e-1-768x510.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SaveTwitter.Net_G7Z1oOQb0AQJI0e-1.jpg 936w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1014px) 100vw, 1014px\">\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>这两件事看似没关系，其实本质上都是同一场地震。</p>\n  <p>Netflix 买华纳大概率是要把好莱坞的百年基业变成更高效的「内容流水线」。而 Tilly 的出现，是为了把不可控的「人」变成可控的「数字资产」。</p>\n  <p>不过，你也别哀叹 AI 要「杀死」好莱坞，别忘了，好莱坞本身就是靠「杀死」前辈起家的。</p>\n  <p>20 世纪初，当电影刚刚兴起时，戏剧界谴责它廉价、粗俗、缺乏艺术性。但正是这种「廉价」和「粗俗」，让更多普通人能够接触到故事和表演，最终催生出了一种全新的艺术形式。</p>\n  <p>更有意思的是，那些今天被我们奉为经典的好莱坞黄金时代作品，当年也是工业流水线的产物。米高梅、派拉蒙、华纳兄弟这些片厂签约演员，量产类型片，用明星制度和宣发机器操控市场。直到 1948 年最高法院的「派拉蒙案」打破片厂垄断，好莱坞才逐渐进入了所谓的「作者电影」时代。</p>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div class=\"image-uploaded gallery old-record-id-AxnqdiT4LoBomYxKMi4c3wrOnkd\" data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;a1465d1e-f4dc-4558-aaf8-f4105d2f39b6&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:2304,&quot;width&quot;:3456,&quot;currHeight&quot;:2304,&quot;currWidth&quot;:3456,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:2304,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:3456,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FMuJVblmz5oRtsGxLJUccEOmlnTb%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;MuJVblmz5oRtsGxLJUccEOmlnTb&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:6274002,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1648030\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/HollywoodSign-360x240.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"998\" height=\"665\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/HollywoodSign-360x240.jpg!720 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/HollywoodSign-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/HollywoodSign-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px\">\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div data-page-id=\"PiDpdnB2OoDt9GxrZS2ccR7enYf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n   <div data-type=\"image\" data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;3d128f6b-d0dc-4c2f-95be-e21af823ec40&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:2304,&quot;width&quot;:3456,&quot;currHeight&quot;:2304,&quot;currWidth&quot;:3456,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:2304,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:3456,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FZxuDbkMcEojbH3xfcufcwj6inlc%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;ZxuDbkMcEojbH3xfcufcwj6inlc&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:6274002,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\">\n    <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n     <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n      <p>▲ 图片来自：维基百科</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>从这个角度看，AI 演员的出现，也并非史无前例的威胁，当年配音技术的成熟，不也让无数默片时代的演员失业了吗？但电影并没有因此变得更糟，反而诞生了《乱世佳人》《卡萨布兰卡》这样的杰作。</p>\n  <p><strong>或许正是那些看似「毁灭」创作的技术，催生出了新的创作可能性。</strong>想象一下：一个导演可以让 Tilly 出演一个 80 岁老妇人，然后在同一部电影里让她回到 18 岁的模样，而不需要任何特效化妆或年龄替身。</p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深描了首位 AI 女演员 Tilly Norwood 的创作过程、技术细节及其引发的好莱坞关于 AI 冲击演员肖像权与行业变革的深度讨论。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深描了首位 AI 女演员 Tilly Norwood 的创作过程、技术细节及其引发的好莱坞关于 AI 冲击演员肖像权与行业变革的深度讨论。",
